eepcopy.go for core/v1 types and staging/src/k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/apis/meta/v1/zz_generated.deepcopy.go for meta/v1 types.\n\nThis import chain is crucial for Kubernetes' type system, as it enables all API objects to be serialized, deserialized, and managed through the runtime.Scheme."
